<!-- ============================================================
   snippets/why99-box.liquid
   Explains the ₹99 advance payment system
   ============================================================ -->

{%- assign advance_raw = settings.advance_amount | default: 99 | plus: 0 -%}
{%- assign advance_cents = advance_raw | times: 100 -%}
{%- assign product_obj = product | default: section.settings.product -%}

{%- if product_obj -%}
  {%- assign remaining = product_obj.price | minus: advance_cents -%}
{%- else -%}
  {%- assign remaining = 140000 | minus: advance_cents -%}
{%- endif -%}

{%- assign city = settings.city | default: 'Hyderabad' -%}

<div class="why99-box">
  <div class="why99-title">💡 Why do we ask for ₹{{ advance_raw }}?</div>
  <div class="why99-explanation">
    We deliver across {{ city }} with open box COD. In the past, some customers placed fake orders for timepass —
    our delivery person would travel across the city, and the customer wouldn't answer the door. 
    This wasted large amount of time and money.
    <br><br>
    If we ask {{ advance_raw }} rs from fake persons they won't pay because they don't take product but genuine members pay's {{ advance_raw }} 
    because they really want product and {{ advance_raw }} rupees is not extra it will be decreased in final amount
    (product cost {% if product_obj %}{{ product_obj.price | money_without_trailing_zeros }}{% else %}₹1,400{% endif %})
    ({{ advance_raw }} pay advance remaining {{ remaining | money_without_trailing_zeros }} at delivery time) no extra paying this just to avoid fake orders only.
  </div>
  <div class="why99-steps">
    <div class="why99-step">
      <div class="w99-icon">1</div>
      <div><strong>Pay ₹{{ advance_raw }} now</strong> — just to avoid fake orders confirms you're genuine</div>
    </div>
    <div class="why99-step">
      <div class="w99-icon">2</div>
      <div>We call you within <strong>30 minutes</strong> and confirm delivery time</div>
    </div>
    <div class="why99-step">
      <div class="w99-icon">3</div>
      <div>Delivery arrives — you <strong>open & fully check</strong> the product first</div>
    </div>
    <div class="why99-step">
      <div class="w99-icon">4</div>
      <div>Happy? Pay <strong>{{ remaining | money_without_trailing_zeros }} cash</strong> to delivery person. Done!</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="why99-refund">
    ✅ Not satisfied? We take the product back. Full ₹{{ advance_raw }} refunded. No questions, no drama.
  </div>
</div>
